===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*bʰewg-|id=enjoy}}
From {{der|en|LL.|perfunctōrius}}, from the past participial stem of {{m|la||[[perfungor]], perfunct-|perform, carry through}}, from {{m|la|per-}} + {{m|la|fungor}}.

